<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fa">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>داشبورد کاربر</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            font-family: 'Tahoma', sans-serif;
            direction: rtl;
            text-align: right;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .dashboard-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .dashboard-card {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 600px;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .dashboard-left {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff416c, #ff4b2b);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .dashboard-left h2 {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .list-group {
            width: 100%;
        }
        .list-group-item a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        .list-group-item a:hover {
            background: #ff4b2b;
            color: white;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        .logout {
            color: red;
        }
        media (min-width: 768px) {
            .dashboard-card {
                flex-direction: row;
                width: 60%;
                text-align: right;
            }
            .dashboard-left {
                flex: 1;
                padding: 40px;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                margin-bottom: 0;
            }
            .dashboard-right {
                flex: 1;
                padding: 40px;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                justify-content: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="dashboard-container">
        <div class="dashboard-card">
            <div class="dashboard-left">
                <h2>سلام، @ViewBag.UserName!</h2>
                <p>به داشبورد خود خوش آمدید</p>
            </div>
            <div class="dashboard-right">
                <ul class="list-group">
                    <li class="list-group-item"><a href="@Url.Action("Profile", "User")">مشاهده اطلاعات شخصی</a></li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><a href="@Url.Action("Loans", "User")">مشاهده وام‌های دریافتی</a></li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><a href="@Url.Action("Payments", "User")">مشاهده پرداخت‌ها</a></li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><a href="@Url.Action("Logout", "Account")" class="logout">خروج از حساب</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
